  "general_information": "The SABRE TRADER is a container vessel built by Yangzijiang Shipbuilding Group for Lomar Shipping. It has a capacity of 1,770teu and features a high level of reefer containers with up to 492 plugs. The ship was delivered in September 2018 and is equipped with an optimised hull form, direct drive propulsion system, and energy-saving devices. It also meets the EEDI Phase 3 ratings 12 years ahead of schedule.",
